{"tid":1705213,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[留意多圖]西灣河交警係用槍指向白褸手足頸部，先再射黑衫","createTime":"2019-11-11T00:42:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T01:02:53.000Z","uid":136992,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"051a7593d86c597d2c9272ef4ce89aa8e9132d8c","tid":1705213,"uid":136992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T00:42:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qM6M3hC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqM6M3hC.png&h=804707a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記者圖片 交警<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/11/082428_ba91d8b403085dd7775e8000e30bdea8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F11%2F082428_ba91d8b403085dd7775e8000e30bdea8.png&h=59fff0ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拔槍 白褸在樓梯底<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9dQ6iRk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9dQ6iRk.png&h=783fda61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n白褸舉槍後並無撤退 數秒內<br />\n白褸慢步行去行人路邊 單腳<br />\n交警舉槍指向白褸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KUSwuYQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKUSwuYQ.png&h=f9e6719d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n白褸行去行人路邊 雙腳落地<br />\n交警踏前 槍指心胸位置<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nSA6iSF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnSA6iSF.png&h=39e3de73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n白褸沒任何攻擊行動 向前踏一少步<br />\n交警用槍[size=6]零距離[size=6]指心胸位置<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5XBpPZN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5XBpPZN.png&h=14da94e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n交警想做拘捕行動 持槍指向白褸頸部 <br />\n再扭動其身體<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3EB5zrU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3EB5zrU.png&h=f8ab3280&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n交警環抱白褸手足<br />\n開第一槍 𣈴冰袖手足左上胸 打中近左中腹<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LKMk7Nj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLKMk7Nj.png&h=1946aed7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第二 三槍 向紫袋手足 但影唔到有無中<br />\n但事後講到名<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3sgk7NE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3sgk7NE.png&h=2a97d445&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bOC8xeo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbOC8xeo.png&h=f098cf15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冰袖手足最後坐到起身 跑到幾步想逃走<br />\n希望無事<br />\n<br />\n結論：<br />\n交警係自身無受攻擊威脅，<br />\n在和手足距離有一段路程上，無用警棍，相反係鬧市舉槍同近距離開槍。當時交警理應同721黨鐵站警一樣逃離現場，等待增援。<br />\n最嚴重係交警近距離 零距離指向市民心胸同頸部位置，絕對係想射殺市民"},{"pid":"f1d62504290d195c8970c68950e1d000bb9b478d","tid":1705213,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T00:43:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ff988d8eb608b68a94703e4e8c54d73ba797b29","tid":1705213,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T00:44:25.000Z","msg":"乜都無做，條交通曱甴舉槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e063ee3dee8f1967f07d225c344770dd5e744751","tid":1705213,"uid":2784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T00:44:48.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 根本就恐怖分子脅持人質"},{"pid":"9619c1cd4e3f57852d6050d3e68333e2179bf560","tid":1705213,"uid":136992,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T00:45:21.000Z","msg":"白褸手足真係好撚用<br />\n冰袖手足都係"},{"pid":"eb6b4e58892cdeefc9a56a06a29e5b4f2b968a72","tid":1705213,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T00:46:28.000Z","msg":"呢個擺明係悍匪呀 恐怖分子先會咁樣做"},{"pid":"1f854d4c0652c34b748c94a81241cece8bdc9cbd","tid":1705213,"uid":131121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T00:46:29.000Z","msg":"香港黑警 殺人如麻"},{"pid":"408863d6af05a4be9d1b93447bd375986c9b7287","tid":1705213,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T00:46:46.000Z","